%2F000020002100A0704719.php&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAwkward+silence\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite id=\"CITEREFStefan_H._Krieger2001\" class=\"citation\">Stefan H. Krieger (Spring 2001), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.law.uoregon.edu/org/olr/archives/80/80_Or_L_Rev_199.pdf\">\"A Time to Keep Silent and a Time to Speak\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>, <i>Oregon Law Review</i>, <b>80</b> (1)</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Oregon+Law+Review&amp;rft.atitle=A+Time+to+Keep+Silent+and+a+Time+to+Speak&amp;rft.ssn=spring&amp;rft.volume=80&amp;rft.issue=1&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.au=Stefan+H.+Krieger&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.law.uoregon.edu%2Forg%2Folr%2Farchives%2F80%2F80_Or_L_Rev_199.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAwkward+silence\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"https://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/Pulp_Fiction#Dialogue\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikiquote:Pulp Fiction\">Wikiquote:Pulp Fiction#Dialogue</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9HQj-G4F9OI\"><span class=\"plainlinks\">The Late Late Show with Craig Ferguson awkward pauses</span></a> on <a href=\"/wiki/YouTube\" title=\"YouTube\">YouTube</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Further_reading\">Further reading</span><span class=\"mw